 Gulasatree Michalsky）（圖/翻攝自ig@gulasatree）\"><figcaption>30歲泰國女星兼模特兒克莉絲汀（Christine Gulasatree Michalsky）（圖/翻攝自ig@gulasatree）</figcaption></figure><p>延伸閱讀：</p><p>沒性行為也中！當兵共用毛巾染菜花　醫揭看診沒戴口罩「鼻孔也長」</p><p>【本文獲「TVBS新聞網」授權轉載。】</p></body></html>","scraped_at":"2026-04-29T03:16:17.399413+00:00","quality":{"score":3,"chars":2054,"images":24,"source":"HK01 國際","fallback":"none"}}